- array for words

- randomly choose array
- once array is chosen, make it unable to chosen again



- user chooses a letter

-if the letter is in the array it is displayed in the same index position

- if the letter is not in the array display part of the hangman

- repeat until the array is full

- if they finish the array before the hangman is complete user wins

- if hangman is complete before array is finished computer wins



